       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION. 
       PROGRAM-ID. Youssouf.
       
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT TEST-FILE ASSIGN TO DD-TFILE
           FILE STATUS IS TESTST.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD TEST-FILE.

       01 REC-TEST-FILE.
           05 EMP-ID PIC X(10).
           05 EMP-NAME PIC X(20).
