           INITIALIZE TESTST.
           OPEN OUTPUT TEST-FILE.
           IF TEST-STATUS = "00"
           DISPLAY "FILE OPEN SUCCESSFUL"
           ELSE
           DISPLAY "FILE OPENING ERROR".